        "message": "Hi {{ $json.name }},<br><br>Thanks for your interest in LeadIntel!<br><br>While we review your request, feel free to check out our <a href=\"#\">documentation</a>.<br><br>We recommend starting with our Starter or Pro tiers to get a feel for the platform. If your needs change or you'd like to schedule a follow-up, just reply to this email!<br><br>Best,<br>The LeadIntel Team",
